title: Paddle War Deluxe
content:
Allright, I finished the game up, and also included a recorded game of me and skypestb2... Check it out.

Some features you might like:

- Take screenshots
- Configure the game
- Record Games - and watch them later
- Original IMF Adlib Music

I sent the game in e-mail to Xtraverse, who will host it. Let's hope he turns up soon...
------------------------------------------------------
Keep in mind, I'm not an artist.

When the master said "Kaputt!", the end of the Great War could be felt.
